---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Wise Energy Pros" description="Privacy Policy for Wise Energy Pros website inquiries and service requests." lang="en">
	<section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-50 md:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">Effective date: March 20, 2026</p>
			<p class="mt-6 text-slate-400">
				Wise Energy Pros values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, how we protect it, and what choices you have when using our website and contacting us for services.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">1. Information We Collect</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">We may collect the following information when you interact with our website or team:</p>
			<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-400">
				<li>Contact details, including name, email address, and phone number.</li>
				<li>Service request details, including project type, property context, and message content.</li>
				<li>Communication preferences, including consent choices for calls, email, and SMS.</li>
				<li>Basic technical data, such as browser/device information and pages visited.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">2. How We Use Information</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">We use collected information to:</p>
			<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-400">
				<li>Respond to inquiries and provide estimates or project follow-up.</li>
				<li>Schedule consultations, site visits, and service communications.</li>
				<li>Improve website performance, user experience, and support quality.</li>
				<li>Comply with legal, regulatory, and safety obligations.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">3. Consent and Communications</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				When you submit a form, you may consent to receive communications related to your inquiry and services. You can opt out of promotional communications at any time by replying with an unsubscribe request or contacting us directly.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">4. Data Sharing</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				We do not sell personal information. We may share limited information with trusted service providers that help us operate our business, such as hosting, analytics, customer communication tools, and scheduling systems, only as needed to support services.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">5. Data Retention</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				We retain information only as long as necessary for business, legal, and operational purposes, including project records, compliance documentation, and customer support follow-up.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">6. Security Measures</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards to protect information from unauthorized access, misuse, alteration, or disclosure. No online platform is completely risk-free, but we apply practical controls appropriate to our operations.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">7. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to request:</p>
			<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-400">
				<li>Access to personal information we hold about you.</li>
				<li>Correction of inaccurate or incomplete information.</li>
				<li>Deletion of information where legally permissible.</li>
				<li>Restriction of certain processing activities.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">8. Third-Party Links and Tools</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Our website may include links or embedded tools from third parties, such as maps or social platforms. Their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">9. Children’s Privacy</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Our services are intended for adults and property decision-makers. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">10. Policy Updates</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect legal, technical, or operational changes. Any updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">11. Contact</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				If you have privacy questions or requests, contact Wise Energy Pros at
				<a href="mailto:intake@wiseenergypros.com" class="font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-cyan-200">intake@wiseenergypros.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
